# Linear Ticket Skill Preference

When the user asks to work on a Linear issue or references a Helio Linear ticket (for example `HEL-5`), prefer using the project skill `linear-ticket-delivery`.

Apply that skill to guide the workflow for:

- reading the ticket first
- asking clarifying questions
- creating the ticket branch
- using `opsx-propose` or `opsx-explore`
- enforcing approval gates
- implementing and verifying changes
- updating relevant artifacts
- archiving with `opsx-archive`
- creating the PR
- updating Linear status/comments through completion

Do not force the skill when the user is clearly asking for something smaller or outside the Linear workflow.
